title: Nordo in for PA! Bercich/Russo/Falness/Grimm/Gellner
description: Eric Nordquist fills in for PA! Pete Bercich talks about the Minneapolis Miracle and this year's NFL Playoffs. The Athletic's Michael Russo calls in from Philly to talk about the Wild playing their worst game ever. Also, the Wild Radio Network's Kevin Falness stops by the studio for more puck talk, Gophers VOX Mike Grimm talks hoops, and FOX Sports North's Marney Gellner talks Wolves and Twins!
